                            <comment id="13012571" author="rhillegas" created="Tue, 29 Mar 2011 17:38:51 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Attaching derby-5162-01-aa-restoreToNull.diff. This is a 1-line patch to SQLChar.restoreToNull() which fixes this bug. I will run regression tests. I don&apos;t propose to write a separate regression test for this problem. This fix should be covered by the more exhaustive test supplied in derby-2515-01-ac-copyINOUTreturnValues.diff.&lt;/p&gt;

